<div class="jumbotron">
  <!--<img src='http://66.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_me173cvcHZ1r9rnkno4_1280.jpg' alt-"Promo wallet">-->
  <div class="jumbotron__div">
    <p class="jumbotron__text">
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Animi, excepturi, cupiditate, delectus doloribus maiores dicta eligendi rem beatae dolore labore repellat et sequi incidunt harum ad eveniet laboriosam saepe tenetur.
